              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_zigbee_devwiz_reset_intro",
                "text": "The Vera Controller will now begin to reset this device."
              },
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6271_step_6_02",
                "text": "1. Simultaneously press and hold the Up and Down buttons at the same time for 3 seconds to enter the advanced settings menu.<br><br>2. Simultaneously press both the Up and Down buttons once to select the Menu 1.<br><br>3. Press the Up button to select 'OFF'.<br><br>4. Press the Up and Down button at the same time once to reset your thermostat.<br><br>5. Once the reset steps are done press 'Delete Device' button to remove it form the unit."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "static_group": 2,
            "group_text": [
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6271_step_6_11",
                "text": "While your thermostat is being Reset, 'OFF' will blink rapidly and the connectivity icon will be animated. 'OFF' will display solid (not blinking) to indicate that your thermostat has been successfully Reset. \n<br><br>\nIf the Reset process was unsuccessful, 'Err' will be displayed for 3 seconds followed by the 'Off' text changing to 'On'.\n<br><br>\nClick the 'Try Adding It Again' button to begin the process of joining the network."
              }
            ]
          }
